CB4J Tutorial

  This tutorial will show how to use CB4J with a real use case.

  Let's suppose you have a CSV file representing new customers of an e-commerce site.
  Records of this file have the following format :
  customer_id;firstname;lastname;age;birthdate;address;email;

  You have to write a batch to classify these customers according to some business criteria, let's say the number of orders they ordered on the site.
  Te batch must generate a report



